paper_title: Temperature-dependent discovery of BCC refractory multi-principal element alloys: Integrating deep learning and CALPHAD calculations

claims.claim: Using an absolute deviation tolerance of 0.07 per phase, the trained MLP achieves an accuracy of ≈0.89 on the test dataset filtered to 1250 < T < 1450.
instruction: The code loads the trained checkpoint, evaluates the model on the test dataset filtered to 1250 < T < 1450, and prints the accuracy
